text: Lauterach is a market town in the district Bregenz in the Austrian state of Vorarlberg. As of 1 January 2019, it has about 10,200 people lived there. The market town is in the northern part of the Vorarlberg Rhine Valley between Bregenz and Dornbirn. == References == == Other websites == * Lauterach's website Category:Settlements in Vorarlberg
